## I'm Linus and I'm a developer.

I contribute to a lot of open source projects and I also write apps and websites for fun and profit.

## Projects

For an up to date list on what I've been working on lately, check my github profile.

- https://github.com/LinusU

## Contact

If you have reached this site you probably want to get in contact with me in regards to some code, app or website written by me. Please send an email or give me a call, I like most humans (and almost all robots).

- linus@folkdatorn.se
- [+46 70 624 09 10](tel:+46706240910)

## LinusU AB

LinusU AB is my swedish company sometimes used for legal matters, or just for fun.
